scene.message:
Yukino: So this seems to be{nl}
Yuriko's room.{waitkey}{clearbox}For someone so prissy and{nl}
cutesy, this is a room in{nl}
unimaginably bad taste.{waitkey}{clearbox}You know we've come,{nl}
don't you? Then come out!{waitkey}{clearbox}Or are you plotting{nl}
something again?{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: Geez! This is Yuriko's{nl}
room, so you don't have to{nl}
yell that loud - I can hear{waitkey}you just fine!!{waitkey}{clearbox}More importantly, you?{nl}
You've got such a pretty face!{nl}
To make that beauty eternal,{waitkey}why not die here!?{waitkey}{clearbox}Keep living and aging and{nl}
you'll just become a dirty{nl}
old hag!!{waitkey}{clearbox}So! Like Yuriko, die at the{nl}
cutest moment of your life!{nl}
While you're still beautiful~{waitkey}{clearbox}Let's live in this tower!!{nl}
Hey, let's? Hm?{waitkey}{clearbox}It's fun! Surely!! Yuriko{nl}
really thinks coming to this{nl}
tower like the "Snow Queen's{waitkey}mask" said was the right call!{waitkey}{clearbox}Yuriko gets to stay cute,{nl}
stay beautiful, forever{nl}
and ever!{waitkey}{clearbox}But Yuriko's been a little{nl}
bored all alone, and Yuriko{nl}
doesn't wanna fight everyone.{waitkey}Hm? Hm??{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: You... do you{nl}
understand what you're{nl}
even saying?{waitkey}{clearbox}What you gained through{nl}
"death," borrowing the{nl}
"Snow Queen's mask's" power -{waitkey}{clearbox}is "the end of your own{nl}
existence" and "a real world{nl}
without you in it."{waitkey}{clearbox}And nothing more than{nl}
"absolute solitude" in this{nl}
tower. It is by no means{waitkey}any "eternal beauty"!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Fuga? What're you{nl}
saying, Yuriko-chan?{nl}
That means, basically,{waitkey}{clearbox}you got killed by the{nl}
"Snow Queen's mask" and{nl}
became this tower's keeper?{waitkey}{clearbox}I mean, you're already dead,{nl}
so... you might not age,{nl}
maybe...{waitkey}{clearbox}but throwing away your{nl}
"life" and "future" in{nl}
reality{waitkey}{clearbox}- nah, the great me doesn't{nl}
want "eternal beauty" like{nl}
that. Sorry, but hard pass!!{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: Sh-shut up! As if a{nl}
man could understand a{nl}
maiden's heart!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey, what about you? You look{nl}
like the cutest one of this{nl}
bunch.{waitkey}{clearbox}Right? You understand what{nl}
Yuriko-chan's saying, don't{nl}
you? Let's gain "eternal{waitkey}beauty" here together!{waitkey}{clearbox}And stay beautiful...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hard pass.{nl}
Don't mock me!{nl}
Don't lump Ayase in with a{waitkey}{clearbox}super-lame woman like you!!{nl}
So super MMC!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ayase! Doesn't wanna stay{nl}
beautiful even "in death"!{waitkey}{clearbox}What! You just gave up on{nl}
"dying"! And "aging"!!{nl}
And "living"!!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Everything, everything,{nl}
everything! Eeeverything!!{waitkey}{clearbox}You gave up! Ran away!!{nl}
Threw it all out!!!{nl}
You're the worst woman ever!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hmph. Well said, Ayase!{waitkey}{clearbox}Truly, "even a one-inch worm{nl}
has a half-inch soul,"{nl}
as they say.{waitkey}{clearbox}Yuriko, give it up. When even{nl}
Ayase, the one here most{nl}
likely to get along with you,{waitkey}is like this,{waitkey}{clearbox}there's not a single one left{nl}
to lend an ear to your{nl}
nonsense.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Yeah!! Ayase, So Cool!{nl}
Well said! I've gained new{nl}
respect for you!{waitkey}{clearbox}Now, Yuriko. When even Ayase,{nl}
the one most likely to get{nl}
along with you, is like this,{waitkey}{clearbox}there's no one here left to{nl}
lend an ear to your words!{nl}
So, what will you do!!{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: Ngh............{nl}
Y-Yuriko-chan went to all{nl}
the trouble, all the trouble,{waitkey}{clearbox}to try and help everyone!!{nl}
To have fun with everyone,{nl}
with everyone!{waitkey}{clearbox}Why, why won't you{nl}
understand?? You blockheads!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Fine!! That's it!!!{nl}
I won't forgive you anymore!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Yuriko-chan is stroong!!{nl}
Even if you cry and apologize{nl}
later, I won't forgive you!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll beat you so hard even{nl}
your souls after death{nl}
disappear!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Heh...!{nl}
As Nanjo would put it,{nl}
you're a case of "a fool{waitkey}can't be cured but by death"!{waitkey}{clearbox}No, in your case, even dying{nl}
once didn't cure you, it{nl}
seems!{waitkey}{clearbox}Now, come at us! Die once{nl}
more! And cure that{nl}
foolishness! Here we go!{waitkey}{ret}
